usa |url=http://ba.n1info.com/Vijesti/a420566/Naselje-kod-Srebrenika-u-karantinu.html |website=N1 BA |accessdate=29 March 2020 |language=bs-Latn-BA}}</ref> [[Tuzla]],<ref name=\"bhrt.ba\"/> [[\u017divinice]]<ref>{{cite web |title=Devet novih slu\u010dajeva u Tuzlanskom kantonu |url=https://www.atvbl.com/vijesti/bih/devet-novih-slucajeva-u-tuzlanskom-kantonu-29-3-2020 |website=ATV |accessdate=29 March 2020 |language=sr-latn}}</ref>\n| align=\"right\"| 33\n| align=\"right\"| 0\n| align=\"right\"| 0\n|-\n| align=\"left\" style=\"background:#EAECF0\"| [[Una-Sana Canton]]\n| align=\"left\"| [[Biha\u0107]],<ref>{{cite web |title=Biha\u0107: \u017dena koja je umrla u Kantonalnoj bolnici pozitivna na koronavirus |url=https://bhrt.ba/bihac-zena-koja-je-umrla-u-kantonalnoj-bolnici-pozitivna-na-koronavirus/1117342/ |website=BHRT |language=bs-BA |date=21 March 2020}}</ref> [[Bosanska Krupa]],<ref>{{cite web |title=Prvi slu\u010daj korona virusa u Bosanskoj Krupi, 154. u BiH |url=http://ba.n1info.com/Vijesti/a419151/Prvi-slucaj-korona-virusa-u-Bosanskoj-Krupi-154.-u-BiH.html |website=N1 BA |language=bs-Latn-BA}}</ref> [[Bu\u017eim]],<ref>{{cite web |last1=PORTAL |first1=Oslobo\u0111enje |title=Oslobo\u0111enje - Ko su osobe iz USK kojima je danas dijagnosticiran koronavirus: Prvi slu\u010daj zaraze u Bu\u017eimu |url=https://www.oslobodjenje.ba/vijesti/bih/ko-su-osobe-iz-usk-kojima-je-danas-dijagnosticiran-koronavirus-prvi-slucaj-zaraze-u-buzimu-543411 |website=www.oslobodjenje.ba |accessdate=27 March 2020 |language=bs-ba}}</ref> [[Cazin]]<ref>{{cite web |title=Iz Kantonalne bolnice Biha\u0107 potvrdili jedan slu\u010daj zaraze koronavirusom u Cazinu |url=https://www.cazin.net/vijesti/iz-kantonalne-bolnice-bihac-potvrdili-jedan-slucaj-zaraze-koronavirusom-u-cazinu |website=Cazin.NET |accessdate=30 March 2020 |language=en}}</ref>\n| align=\"right\"| 17\n| align=\"right\"| 3\n| align=\"right\"| 0\n|-\n| align=\"left\" style=\"background:#EAECF0\"| [[West Herzegovina Canton]]\n| al