\n| align=\"right\"| 0\n| align=\"right\"| 0\n|-\n| align=\"left\" style=\"background:#EAECF0\"| [[Prnjavor, Bosnia and Herzegovina|Prnjavor]]\n| align=\"right\" | 5\n| align=\"right\" | 0\n| align=\"right\" | 0\n|-\n| align=\"left\" style=\"background:#EAECF0\"| [[Ribnik, Bosnia and Herzegovina|Ribnik]]\n| align=\"right\"| 3\n| align=\"right\"| 1\n| align=\"right\"| 0\n|-\n| align=\"left\" style=\"background:#EAECF0\" | [[Srbac]]\n| align=\"right\" | 1\n| align=\"right\" | 0\n| align=\"right\" | 0\n|-\n| align=\"left\" style=\"background:#EAECF0\" | [[\u0160ekovi\u0107i]]\n| align=\"right\" | 1\n| align=\"right\" | 0\n| align=\"right\" | 0\n|-\n| align=\"left\" style=\"background:#EAECF0\" | [[\u0160ipovo]]\n| align=\"right\" | 1\n| align=\"right\" | 0\n| align=\"right\" | 0\n|-\n| align=\"left\" style=\"background:#EAECF0\" | [[Tesli\u0107]]\n| align=\"right\" | 7\n| align=\"right\" | 0\n| align=\"right\" | 0\n|-\n| align=\"left\" style=\"background:#EAECF0\" | [[Zvornik]]\n| align=\"right\" | 1\n| align=\"right\" | 0\n| align=\"right\" | 0\n|-\n! scope=\"col\" align=\"right\"| Total\n! align=\"right\"| 243\n! align=\"right\"| 3\n! align=\"right\"| 13\n|-\n| colspan=\"5\"|{{small|''As of 1 April 2020}}<ref name=\"JZU Institut za javno zdravstvo RS\" /><ref name=\"koronausrpskoj\" />\n|}\n\nAs of 1 April 2020, people from following [[Cantons of the Federation of Bosnia and Herzegovina|cantons]] and municipalities in the Federation of Bosnia and Herzegovina have been infected:\n\n{| class=\"sortable wikitable\" style=\"text-align:center;\"\n|-\n! scope=\"col\" | Canton\n! scope=\"col\" | Municipalities affected\n! scope=\"col\" | Cases\n! scope=\"col\" | Deaths\n! scope=\"col\" | Recoveries<ref name=\"covid-19.ba\" />\n|-\n| align=\"left\" style=\"background:#EAECF0\"| [[Bosnian-Podrinje Canton Gora\u017ede|Bosnian-Podrinje Canton]]\n| align=\"left\"| [[Gora\u017ede]]<ref>{{cite web |title=Prvi slu\u010daj u Gora\u017edu: Svi koji su bili u kontaktu sa direktoricom 